<span id="freeTextContainer16617797120455680979">Queen Elizabeth gets bitten by the bookworm! Her royal duties suffer, the Prince is baffled, and her staff fears she is declining. But, in reality, the Queen is absorbed in reading 24/7, discussing books, talking with writers, and taking notes. It is a perfectly penned novella with a great ending (she wouldn’t dare!) and it brought me much joy.</span>

          </span>
